# vem_message_generator

### usage for request VEM
#### generate VEM
```shell
go run cmd/main.go --validators 0x123,0x234 --pk 1d073aba70e3e855d409e0f2722d6b3be2399f6b152355596f662aa6d1ba6a84
```
#### decrypt VEM

```shell
# golang usage
go run cmd/vem_request/main.go --ecdhPrivateKey be0ff21fb9df7d0471c2b5c19e2f9a3b1a903753f9dc4ffac5fe86acc38d5af0 --encryptedMessage 

# js usage
node js/index.js --ecdhPrivateKey be0ff21fb9df7d0471c2b5c19e2f9a3b1a903753f9dc4ffac5fe86acc38d5af0 --encryptedMessage 
```

### usage for request prediction of possible VEMs
#### generate request
```shell
go run cmd/vem_prediction/main.go --pk 1d073aba70e3e855d409e0f2722d6b3be2399f6b152355596f662aa6d1ba6a84 --validators 0x123,0x234 --predictedIndex 1,2,3
```

#### decrypt request
```shell
go run cmd/vem_prediction/main.go --ecdhPrivateKey b26447dcc587d3b67f0bcb5d77c3943aaf9f84489460361d3c9055384d72a6bb --encryptedMessage 
```

```shell
node js/index.js --ecdhPrivateKey b26447dcc587d3b67f0bcb5d77c3943aaf9f84489460361d3c9055384d72a6bb --encryptedMessage 
```
